# CodeFlow Build Bridge Rules

- Major runtime changes require a matching `.agents/build-tickets/` ticket.
- Contract-impacting changes require a referenced `.agents/contracts/` file.
- Implement one ticket at a time when practical.
- Write validation evidence to `.agents/reports/`.
- Use `.agents/runbooks/phase-ticket-handoff.md` before implementation and `.agents/runbooks/phase-closeout.md` before declaring a phase done.
- If implementation drifts from a ticket or contract, record the drift and reconcile it explicitly.

